room_title: Escape room "Temple Ruins" by Exithis Pensacola in Pensacola
room_description: After searching the world over, you and your team of explorers have finally made it to the great Aztec temple. You have made it into the final room, now find the Mayan idol and escape the natives before it's too late. Beware of the traps that guard your prize, and be sure to channel the ancient mathematicians along the way. We are counting on you to get it done.
